OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,6,Ftime this morning. The afternoon will
OL,7,Fbe brighter with a few showers, some
OL,8,Fof these heavy but tending to move
OL,9,Fthrough quickly in brisk southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few heavy showers will tend
OL,13,Fto die out this evening. The rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will see further showers
OL,15,Facross western areas, but drier around
OL,16,Fthe east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
