OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,8,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,9,Fbecoming fewer later. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,12,Fcloud developing on Sunday alongside
OL,13,Frisk of showers later. A few showers
OL,14,Fon Monday but mostly dry by Tuesday.
OL,15,FWinds lighter than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
